      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s still got so much life left in it! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is in really solid shape. It's the perfect fit for someone who wants a dependable car that looks great and drives even better without the brand-new price tag. It's been well-loved and well-maintained, ready to hit the road with a new owner. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
