      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L I6 engine. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and proactive rod bearing replacement, addressing critical platform weak points. The S54\u2019s individual throttle bodies provide exceptional throttle response, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable differential lock. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows honest wear typical of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains robust and free of parasitic losses. A performance-first vehicle for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
