    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW M2 finished in stunning Long Beach Blue Metallic. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a driver who wants performance without the showroom-floor price tag. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel, consistent with regular use. Inside, the Black Dakota leather cabin with contrast blue stitching remains firm and clean, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster and no tears or odors. Mechanically, this M2 is robust; it features a complete service log from certified technicians, with the most recent oil service and brake fluid flush performed just 1,200 miles ago. It sits on Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with approximately 6/32\" tread remaining. All electronics, including the iDrive system and Harman Kardon audio, function perfectly. No performance modifications have been made\u2014this is a pure, stock example ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
